        <div xml:id="NA0">
            <lg type="edition">
                <l>mānilañ cēvaṭi yākat tūnīr</l>
                <l>vaḷainaral pauva muṭukkai yāka</l>
                <l>vicumpumey yākat ticaikai yākap</l>
                <l>pacuṅkatir matiyamoṭu cuṭarkaṇ ṇāka</l>
                <l>viyaṉṟa vellām payiṉṟakat taṭakkiya</l>
                <l>vēta mutalva ṉeṉpa</l>
                <l>tītaṟa viḷaṅkiya tikiri yōṉē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>He with the disc which is shining to cut off evil,</l>
<l rend="indent9">they say,</l>
<l>is the first in the Vedas,</l>
<l>who has concealed inside [himself and] who resides in all that is:</l>
<l rend="indent">that [his] eyes are the sun with the fresh-rayed moon,</l>
<l rend="indent">that [his] hands are the [four] directions, that [his] body</l>
<l rend="indent">is the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">that [his] garment is the ocean that [re]sounds in conches,</l>
<l rend="indent">of pure water, that [his] red feet are the great land.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
